c: 7
v: 27
t: “E inu ana a Adam! Satana asakusokonezeni monga momwe adawatulutsira makolo anu m’Munda wamtendere ndi kuwavula onse awiri chovala chawo kuti awasonyeze umaliseche wawo. Ndithu iye ndi mtundu wake akukuonani pomwe inu simukuwaona. Ndithu asatana tawachita kukhala abwenzi a osakhulupirira